\id 3JN Bambam 3 John, South Sulawesi Indonesia 
\h 3 Yohanes 
\toc1 Kapentallunna Suha'na Yohanes 
\toc2 3 Yohanes 
\toc3 3Yoh. 
\mt1 Kapentallunna Suha'na Yohanes  
\imt1 Bätäna issinna  
\ip Inde suha' natuli' Yohanes to disangai “Pebaba Ada'” napakatuam mesa pebaba ada' illaam jumaa', isanga Gayus. Yohanes umpuji Gayus aka si umbalii solana to Sahani indo to si lao umpa'pakahebaam Kaheba Katilallasam lako botto senga'. Anna napakainga'pi duka' diona pa'palakoam kadakena mesa tau isanga Diotrefes.  
\iot Lesoanna issinna  
\io1 1. Kada passu'bä' (1:1-4)  
\io1 2. To umpa'pakahebaam sanganna Kristus pahallu dipamoloi (1:5-12)  
\io1 3. Kada pebubum (1:13-15)  
\ie  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Kao Pebaba Ada' untuli'i inde suha' lu lako Gayus to kupakamaja anna to kukamasei si'da-si'da.   
\p
\v 2 O solaku to kupakamaja, kupa'sambajangangko anna mala masakke liuko anna masannam illaam ingganna-ingganna sia, la susi mapianna busäsam penabammu.  
\v 3 Tilalla' punalaä' tappana sule inde sanaka-naka solasubunta natulasannä' diona kamanontongammu muanda'i kamaloloanna Puang Allataala, aka si ma'palakongko situhu' kamaloloam ia too.  
\v 4 Tä'um deem la susi katilallasangku tappana kupelele diua ma'palakom ingganna änä'ku situhu' kamaloloam.   
\s1 To umpa'pakahebaam sanganna Kristus pahallu dipamoloi  
\sr 5-12  
\p
\v 5 O solaku to kupakamaja, tä' deem pada samapia kamanontongammu si umbalii solasubunta to matappa', moinna anna tä'pokoa' siissangam.  
\v 6 Anna puham natulasam lako jumaa'ki diona pa'kamasemu. Kela mala tontä liuko umpamoloi itim tau ke mengkalaoim anna mala tä' deem kakuhängam illaam pa'laoanna. Maka' too umpateemmi, la sipäto'um dio olona Puang Allataala indo pa'palakoammu.  
\v 7 Aka illaam pa'laoanna umpa'pakahebaam sanganna Kristus, tä' deem aka-aka la natahima dio mai to tamuissam Puang Allataala.  
\v 8 Dadi kita to matappa', la pahalluki' umpamoloi tau ia too anna mala mangngala tabaki' duka' illaam umpa'pakahebaam kamaloloam.   
\p
\v 9 Deemmi suha' kutuli' kupakatuam jumaa' itim, sapo' tä' liu si napatama tula'ki indo Diotrefes to si maelo' ia handam kuasa.  
\v 10 Dadi sulepä' matim mane kupomakalesoanni jumaa' indo napaboboi bäbäkam tula'. Anna tä' angga mandi ia too si napogau', sapo' si mokapi untahima solasubunta to matappa' anna tä' umpäbäi jumaa' untahima indo solasubunta to matappa'. Anna maka' deem untahimai, si naäläi illaam mai jumaa'.   
\p
\v 11 O solaku to kupakamaja, daa umpehapanni to ma'gau' kadake, sapo' la umpehapanniko to ma'gau' mapia. Menna-menna umpogau' kamapiaam, tau ia too änä'nam Puang Allataala. Sapo' menna-menna si umpogau' kakadakeam, tau ia too tä' ia muissam Puang Allataala.   
\p
\v 12 Anna diona ia Demetrius natula' mapia asam tau. Anna pa'palakoanna duka' umpatandaanni kamapiaanna, aka sihondoi kamaloloanna Puang Allataala. Anna kami' duka' umpa'paissanganni diona kamapiaanna, anna muissanni muua tappa' tula'ki.   
\s1 Kada pebubum  
\sr 13-15  
\p
\v 13 Moinna anna budapi la pahallu kutulasangko, sapo' mokaä' umpaillaam asanni inde suha',  
\v 14 aka maelo'ä' la bale' matim anna sipekaleangki' sipa'tula'.  
\v 15 La naundu' dako too kamasakkeam sola kamasannangam. Salama'na duka' matim ingganna solata inde. Anna la umpalambisannä' duka' salama'ku lako si mesa-mesa solata itim.  
\p Padam too.   